Sentencas: A novel cobalt-free La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.9Nb0.1O3 (LSFNb) cathode material was synthesized by a solid-state reaction.
Titulo: A Novel Cobalt-free La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.9Nb0.1O3 Cathode for Medium Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: And BaCe0.7Zr0.2Sm0.1O3-alpha (BCZSm) electrolyte was prepared by a sol-gel method.
Titulo: A Novel Cobalt-free La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.9Nb0.1O3 Cathode for Medium Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Transmission Electron Microscopy (TEM) and Thermal Gravimetry Analysis-Differential Scanning Calorimetry (TGA-DSC) were used to determine the size and the first sintering temperature of BCZSm, respectively.
Titulo: A Novel Cobalt-free La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.9Nb0.1O3 Cathode for Medium Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The structures of cathode, electrolyte and anode were analyzed via X-ray Diffraction (XRD).
Titulo: A Novel Cobalt-free La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.9Nb0.1O3 Cathode for Medium Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: A thin film fuel cell of LSFNb / BCZSm / NiO-BCZSm was assembled and reached the highest power densities of 109 mW.cm(-2) and 182.6 mW.cm(-2) at 700 degrees C and 800 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: A Novel Cobalt-free La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.9Nb0.1O3 Cathode for Medium Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
